"mb-0.5 flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-[10px] px-2.5 py-2 text-[13px] font-medium text-ink-soft\"><span class=\"flex h-[22px] w-[22px] items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-off2 text-xs\">🔗</span> Share</div><div class=\"mb-0.5 flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-[10px] px-2.5 py-2 text-[13px] font-medium text-ink-soft\"><span class=\"flex h-[22px] w-[22px] items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-off2 text-xs\">⚙️</span> Settings</div><div class=\"mt-6 rounded-xl bg-accent-light px-3 py-3.5 text-left\"><div class=\"mb-1 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[.04em] text-accent\">LIVE SESSION</div><div class=\"font-syne text-xl font-extrabold text-ink\">32</div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-ink-soft\">photos captured</div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-5 p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"font-syne text-lg font-bold text-ink\">Session Gallery</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 rounded-[100px] bg-[#EAF9F1] px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-[#1A8A4A] before:content-[&#x27;●&#x27;] before:text-[8px]\">Session live</div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-2.5 max-[640px]:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#E8EDFF,#C7D0FF)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">🧑‍🤝‍🧑</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#FFE8F0,#FFBED4)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">🎉</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#E8FFF4,#B8F5D8)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">💑</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#FFF8E8,#FFE9B8)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">🥳</div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-2.5 max-[640px]:grid-cols-1\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-off px-4 py-3.5 text-left\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[22px] font-extrabold leading-tight text-ink\">32</div><div class=\"mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-ink-soft\">Photos taken</div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-off px-4 py-3.5 text-left\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[22px] font-extrabold leading-tight text-ink\">18</div><div class=\"mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-ink-soft\">QR shares</div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-off px-4 py-3.5 text-left\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[22px] font-extrabold leading-tight text-ink\">4</div><div class=\"mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-ink-soft\">Templates used</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"flex items-center border-y border-border px-16 py-8 max-[1024px]:flex-col max-[1024px]:items-start max-[1024px]:gap-3 max-[1024px]:px-4\"><span class=\"mr-10 shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.1em] text-ink-soft max-[1024px]:mr-0\">Trusted by</span><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-12\"><span class=\"font-syne text-[15px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink opacity-20\">Lumière Events</span><span class=\"font-syne text-[15px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink opacity-20\">SnapCo Studios</span><span class=\"font-syne text-[15px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink opacity-20\">Bloom Agency</span><span class=\"font-syne text-[15px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink opacity-20\">Flashwave</span><span class=\"font-syne text-[15px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink opacity-20\">Noir Collective</span><span class=\"font-syne text-[15px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink opacity-20\">Studio Eight</span></div></div><section class=\"px-16 py-24 max-[1024px]:px-4\" id=\"features\"><div class=\"mb-14 text-center\"><div class=\"mb-5 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.1em] text-accent before:h-[2px] before:w-5 before:rounded before:bg-accent before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;]\">Features</div><h2 class=\"font-syne text-[clamp(30px,4vw,48px)] font-extrabold leading-[1.4] text-ink\">Everything a modern photobooth<br/>startup needs</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-[480px] text-center text-[17px] font-normal leading-[1.65] text-ink-soft\">Tools built for speed, scale, and a seamless experience — from your first event to your hundredth.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-[1024px]:grid-cols-1\"><div class=\"row-span-2 flex flex-col rounded-radius border border-border bg-off px-9 py-10 transition-shadow hover:shadow-md\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-accent-light text-[22px]\">🎨</div><div class=\"mb-2.5 font-syne text-lg font-bold text-ink\">Custom Template Builder</div><p class=\"text-sm leading-[1.7] text-ink-soft\">Drag-and-drop layouts, brand overlays, and custom frames. Design a photo experience that looks completely on-brand for every client.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex min-h-[180px] flex-1 items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] border border-border bg-white p-5\"><div class=\"grid w-full grid-cols-2 gap-2\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] rounded-[10px] border-2 border-accent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#E8EDFF,#C7D0FF)] text-lg flex items-center justify-center\">🧑‍🤝‍🧑<span class=\"absolute right-1.5 top-1.5 flex h-[18px] w-[18px] items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-[10px] font-bold text-white\">✓</span></div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-[10px] border-2 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE8F0,#FFBED4)] text-lg flex items-center justify-center\">🎉</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-[10px] border-2 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#FFF8E8,#FFE4A0)] text-lg flex items-center justify-center\">💑</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-[10px] border-2 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#E8FFF4,#B8F5D8)] text-lg flex items-center justify-center\">🥳</div></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-radius border border-border bg-white p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-[#FFE8F0] text-[22px]\">✨</div><div class=\"mb-2.5 font-syne text-lg font-bold text-ink\">AI Enhancements</div><p class=\"text-sm leading-[1.7] text-ink-soft\">Background removal, skin smoothing, and live filters — all processed on-device, instantly.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-radius border border-ink bg-ink p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-white/10 text-[22px]\">📲</div><div class=\"mb-2.5 font-syne text-lg font-bold text-white\">Instant Sharing</div><p class=\"text-sm leading-[1.7] text-white/50\">QR codes, SMS, and email delivery in seconds. Guests leave with their photos — your brand in their pocket.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-radius border border-border bg-white p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-[#E8FFF4] text-[22px]\">📊</div><div class=\"mb-2.5 font-syne text-lg font-bold text-ink\">Analytics Dashboard</div><p class=\"text-sm leading-[1.7] text-ink-soft\">Track shares, prints, and engagement across every event to optimize and grow your business.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-radius border border-border bg-white p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-[#FFFAE8] text-[22px]\">🎥</div><div class=\"mb-2.5 font-syne text-lg font-bold text-ink\">Boomerang &amp; GIF Mode</div><p class=\"text-sm leading-[1.7] text-ink-soft\">Give guests something shareable beyond stills. Looping videos and animated GIFs built right in.</p></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-16 grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto] items-center gap-[60px] rounded-3xl bg-ink px-20 py-[72px] max-[1024px]:mx-4 max-[1024px]:grid-cols-1 max-[1024px]:gap-8 max-[1024px]:px-6 max-[1024px]:py-10\"><div><div class=\"mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.1em] text-white/35 before:h-[2px] before:w-5 before:rounded before:bg-white/35 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;]\">Results</div><h2 class=\"max-w-[400px] font-syne text-[clamp(30px,4vw,48px)] font-extrabold leading-[1.4] text-white\">Numbers that<br/>prove the point</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-base text-white/45\">Join thousands of studios running events on Framr Studio every day.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-[640px]:grid-cols-1\"><div class=\"min-w-[150px] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-6 py-7\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[44px] font-extrabold leading-[1.4] text-white\">12<em class=\"not-italic text-accent\">k</em></div><div class=\"mt-2 text-[13px] text-white/40\">Active studios worldwide</div></div><div class=\"min-w-[150px] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-6 py-7\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[44px] font-extrabold leading-[1.4] text-white\">98<em class=\"not-italic text-accent\">%</em></div><div class=\"mt-2 text-[13px] text-white/40\">Uptime SLA guarantee</div></div><div class=\"min-w-[150px] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-6 py-7\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[44px] font-extrabold leading-[1.4] text-white\">3<em class=\"not-italic text-accent\">×</em></div><div class=\"mt-2 text-[13px] text-white/40\">Faster event setup</div></div><div class=\"min-w-[150px] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-6 py-7\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[44px] font-extrabold leading-[1.4] text-white\">4.9<em class=\"not-italic text-accent\">★</em></div><div class=\"mt-2 text-[13px] text-white/40\">Average studio rating</div></div></div></div><section class=\"px-16 py-24 max-[1024px]:px-4\" id=\"how\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 items-center gap-20 max-[1024px]:grid-cols-1 max-[1024px]:gap-8\"><div><div class=\"mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.1em] text-accent before:h-[2px] before:w-5 before:rounded before:bg-accent before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;]\">How it works</div><h2 class=\"font-syne text-[clamp(30px,4vw,48px)] font-extrabold leading-[1.25] text-ink\">Up and running in<br/>minutes, not days</h2><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col\"><div class=\"cursor-pointer border-b border-border py-6 last:border-b-0\"><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-bold transition-all border-accent bg-accent text-white\">1</div><div><div class=\"mb-2 font-syne text-base font-bold transition-colors text-ink\">Create your event</div><div class=\"text-sm leading-[1.65] text-ink-soft\">Name your event, pick your layout, and choose a template. Takes under two minutes.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"cursor-pointer border-b border-border py-6 last:border-b-0\"><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-bold transition-all border-border-strong text-ink-soft\">2</div><div><div class=\"mb-2 font-syne text-base font-bold transition-colors text-ink-soft\">Customize your branding</div><div class=\"text-sm leading-[1.65] text-ink-soft\">Add your logo, colors, and overlays. Real-time preview shows exactly what guests will see.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"cursor-pointer border-b border-border py-6 last:border-b-0\"><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-bold transition-all border-border-strong text-ink-soft\">3</div><div><div class=\"mb-2 font-syne text-base font-bold transition-colors text-ink-soft\">Go live &amp; capture</div><div class=\"text-sm leading-[1.65] text-ink-soft\">Connect your camera or use your tablet&#x27;s built-in. Framr handles capture and processing automatically.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"cursor-pointer border-b border-border py-6 last:border-b-0\"><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-xs font-bold transition-all border-border-strong text-ink-soft\">4</div><div><div class=\"mb-2 font-syne text-base font-bold transition-colors text-ink-soft\">Share &amp; review results</div><div class=\"text-sm leading-[1.65] text-ink-soft\">Guests share instantly via QR. You get a full analytics report after every session.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-border bg-off p-9 shadow-md\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-border bg-off px-4 py-3 text-xs font-semibold text-ink-soft\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center\"><span class=\"mr-1.5 inline-block h-[7px] w-[7px] animate-pulse rounded-full bg-[#27AE60]\"></span>Live Preview</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-accent\">2×2 Grid</span></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 p-5\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#E8EDFF,#C7D0FF)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">😄</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#FFE8F0,#FFBED4)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">🎊</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#E8FFF4,#B8F5D8)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">💃</div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg bg-[linear-gradient(145deg,#FFF8E8,#FFE4A0)] text-[22px] flex items-center justify-center\">🥂</div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-t border-border px-5 py-3.5 text-xs\"><span class=\"font-medium text-ink-soft\">Session: <strong class=\"text-ink\">Wedding Co.</strong></span><button class=\"cursor-pointer rounded-[100px] border-none bg-accent px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white\">Share via QR</button></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2.5\"><div class=\"rounded-[14px] border border-border bg-white p-4\"><div class=\"font-syne text-[22px] font-extrabold text-ink\">14s</div><div class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-ink-soft\">Avg. setup time</div></div><div class=\"rounded