ne text-[clamp(30px,4vw,48px)] font-extrabold leading-[1.25] text-ink\">Founders love Framr Studio</h2></div><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-[1040px] grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-[1024px]:grid-cols-1\"><div class=\"rounded-[20px] border border-border bg-off p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-sm\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-[13px] tracking-[2px] text-[#F59E0B]\">★★★★★</div><div class=\"mb-6 text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-ink\">&quot;We launched our photobooth startup in 3 weeks. Framr Studio handled everything — templates, sharing, analytics. It just works.&quot;</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,theme(colors.accent),#8B8FFF)] font-syne text-sm font-extrabold text-white\">SA</div><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-ink\">Sofia Andreou</div><div class=\"text-xs text-ink-soft\">Founder, Lumière Photo Booths</div></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[20px] border border-border bg-off p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-sm\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-[13px] tracking-[2px] text-[#F59E0B]\">★★★★★</div><div class=\"mb-6 text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-ink\">&quot;The AI background removal alone changed how we pitch to corporate clients. It&#x27;s a premium feature that closes deals.&quot;</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,theme(colors.accent2),#FF9AB8)] font-syne text-sm font-extrabold text-white\">ML</div><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-ink\">Marcus Leite</div><div class=\"text-xs text-ink-soft\">CEO, SnapCo Studios</div></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[20px] border border-border bg-off p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-sm\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-[13px] tracking-[2px] text-[#F59E0B]\">★★★★★</div><div class=\"mb-6 text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-ink\">&quot;We run 20+ events a month and Framr&#x27;s analytics finally showed us what&